Building on Windows
===================

Requirements
------------

Visual C++ 6.0
Perl (ActivePerl)
CMake 2.6 (or higher)

Build process
-------------

Open a command prompt, and change directory to the ofsystem source
directory.

To build using NMake

> cmake -G "NMake Makefiles"
> nmake

To build using Visual Studio

> cmake -G "Visual Studio 6"

Open the .dsw file in Visual Studio, and press F7 to build all.
